# Enhanced Decentralized AI Model Registry and Ranking Platform
A comprehensive smart contract built on the Stacks blockchain that enables decentralized registration, community-driven evaluation, and reputation-based ranking of AI models.

##  Overview
This smart contract creates a trustless platform where AI researchers and developers can register their models, receive community feedback, and build reputation through quality contributions. The system uses economic incentives and weighted voting to ensure high-quality evaluations and prevent spam.

##  Key Features
###  Model Registration
- **Stake-based Registration**: Requires 1 STX minimum stake to register models
- **IPFS Integration**: Store model content and metadata on IPFS
- **Category Classification**: Support for 8 AI model categories
- **Time-locked Withdrawals**: 100 blocks lockup period for stake security

###  Community Evaluation
- **Weighted Voting System**: Reputation-based scoring mechanism
- **Rating Scale**: 1-10 point evaluation system
- **Anti-Spam Protection**: One evaluation per user per model
- **Comment System**: Optional feedback with length validation

###  Reputation & Ranking
- **Dynamic Leaderboards**: Category-specific model rankings
- **Reputation Points**: Earned through contributions and evaluations
- **Performance Analytics**: Weekly/monthly evaluation tracking
- **Quality Metrics**: Consistency and trending scores

##  Architecture
### Smart Contract Components

```
├── Constants & Configuration
│   ├── Economic Parameters (stake amounts, lockup periods)
│   ├── Platform Limits (string lengths, model counts)
│   └── Supported Categories (8 AI model types)
├── Data Structures
│   ├── Model Registry (registration details, scores)
│   ├── Evaluation Records (votes, comments, timestamps)
│   ├── Stake Balances (economic tracking)
│   ├── Leaderboards (category rankings)
│   └── Reputation Profiles (user activity)
└── Functions
    ├── Public Functions (register, evaluate, withdraw)
    ├── Read-only Queries (fetch data)
    ├── Administrative (model deactivation)
    └── Private Helpers (internal logic)
```

##  Getting Started
### Prerequisites
- Stacks blockchain access
- STX tokens for staking
- IPFS for content storage

### Deployment
1. Deploy the contract to Stacks blockchain
2. Initialize platform categories:
   ```clarity
   (contract-call? .ai-model-registry initialize-platform-categories)
   ```

### Basic Usage
#### Register an AI Model
```clarity
(contract-call? .ai-model-registry register-artificial-intelligence-model
  "My NLP Model"
  "Advanced natural language processing model for sentiment analysis"
  "natural-language-processing"
  "QmYourIPFSHashHere1234567890abcdef1234567890abcdef12345678"
)
```

#### Submit Model Evaluation
```clarity
(contract-call? .ai-model-registry submit-community-model-evaluation
  u1  ;; model-id
  u8  ;; rating (1-10)
  (some "Excellent performance on benchmark tests!")
)
```

#### Withdraw Stake (after lockup period)
```clarity
(contract-call? .ai-model-registry withdraw-model-registration-stake u1)
```

##  Supported AI Model Categories

1. **Natural Language Processing** - Text analysis, translation, chatbots
2. **Computer Vision** - Image recognition, object detection
3. **Recommendation Systems** - Personalization, content filtering
4. **Reinforcement Learning** - Game AI, robotics, optimization
5. **Generative Models** - Content creation, GANs, VAEs
6. **Speech Recognition** - Voice processing, transcription
7. **Time Series Analysis** - Forecasting, pattern recognition
8. **Other Category** - Miscellaneous AI applications

##  Query Functions
### Model Information
```clarity
;; Get complete model details
(contract-call? .ai-model-registry fetch-complete-model-details u1)

;; Check model status
(contract-call? .ai-model-registry verify-model-current-active-status u1)

;; Get category leaderboard
(contract-call? .ai-model-registry fetch-category-based-leaderboard "computer-vision")
```

### User Data
```clarity
;; Get user reputation profile
(contract-call? .ai-model-registry fetch-participant-reputation-profile 'ST1PQHQKV0RJXZFY1DGX8MNSNYVE3VGZJSRTPGZGM)

;; Get user's stake balance
(contract-call? .ai-model-registry fetch-participant-total-stake-balance 'ST1PQHQKV0RJXZFY1DGX8MNSNYVE3VGZJSRTPGZGM)

;; Get user's evaluation for a model
(contract-call? .ai-model-registry fetch-user-model-evaluation 'ST1PQHQKV0RJXZFY1DGX8MNSNYVE3VGZJSRTPGZGM u1)
```

##  Configuration Parameters
| Parameter | Value | Description |
|-----------|-------|-------------|
| Minimum Stake | 1 STX | Required to register a model |
| Lockup Period | 100 blocks | Withdrawal delay after registration |
| Max Rating | 10 | Highest evaluation score |
| Min Rating | 1 | Lowest evaluation score |
| Max Models/Category | 10 | Leaderboard limit |
| Reputation Weight | 100 | Scoring multiplier |

##  Security Features
### Economic Security
- **Stake Requirements**: Economic barrier to entry
- **Time Locks**: Prevent immediate withdrawals
- **Reputation Weighting**: Higher reputation = more influence

### Input Validation
- String length validation
- Rating bounds checking
- Category verification
- IPFS hash format validation

### Access Control
- Model creator authorization
- Admin-only functions
- Duplicate prevention

##  Reputation System
### Earning Points
- **Model Registration**: +5 reputation points
- **Evaluation Submission**: +1 reputation point
- **Quality Contributions**: Bonus points (future implementation)

### Reputation Benefits
- **Weighted Voting**: Higher reputation = more influence
- **Platform Recognition**: Leaderboard visibility
- **Future Rewards**: Economic incentives (roadmap)

##  Error Codes

| Code | Error | Description |
|------|-------|-------------|
| u100 | ERR-UNAUTHORIZED-ACCESS-DENIED | Insufficient permissions |
| u101 | ERR-MODEL-REGISTRATION-NOT-FOUND | Model doesn't exist |
| u102 | ERR-DUPLICATE-EVALUATION-SUBMISSION | Already evaluated |
| u103 | ERR-INVALID-RATING-SCORE-PROVIDED | Rating out of bounds |
| u104 | ERR-MODEL-ALREADY-EXISTS | Duplicate registration |
| u105 | ERR-INSUFFICIENT-STAKE-AMOUNT | Not enough STX |
| u106 | ERR-INVALID-MODEL-CATEGORY-TYPE | Unsupported category |
| u107 | ERR-MODEL-STATUS-DEACTIVATED | Model is inactive |
| u108 | ERR-WITHDRAWAL-TIME-LOCK-ACTIVE | Lockup period active |
| u109 | ERR-INVALID-STRING-LENGTH-PROVIDED | String validation failed |
| u110 | ERR-INVALID-COMMENT-LENGTH-EXCEEDED | Comment too long |

